{"word":"γραῦς","slug":"γραῦς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>γραῦς</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from same Root as <a href='S:γέρων'><el>γέρων</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>an old woman</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>; <el>γρ. παλαιή</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <el>γραῦς γυνή</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>scum</i>, as of boiled milk, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}